教學方法 Teaching Strategies
      The course is in a problem-based learning (PBL) format, containing lecture and paper discussion. Students can select one studing area coordinated by the following professors :
Dr. Shainn-Wei Wang : RNA viruses and host factors interaction
Dr. Ching-Hao Teng : Microbial genetics and pathogenesis
Dr. Christina L. Chang: Tumor transformation/Neronal differentiation/DNA damage and repair    

		※請遵守智慧財產權觀念  不得不法影印
		 Please follow the Intellectual Property instruction and No illegal copy
	

