核心能力 Competence
■ 閱讀、理解與運用專業知識
培養學生具備一般及專業領域的研究素養，並富有國際視野之科學涵養 Good reading comprehension on scientific materials and excellent capabilities in applying the learned professional knowledge
To train students to have good backgrounds in general and specialized fields and have global views of science■ 彙整新知與良好的溝通能力
培養學生具備彙整分子醫學新知與溝通表達研究成果的能力 Abilities of updating and organizing innovative knowledge and demonstrating good communicational skills
To train students to learn efficiently and to apply their knowledge effectively■ 具備操作生科技術的能力
培養學生具備專業技術及專業能力 Capabilities of using techniques in life science
To train students to acquire both in breadth and in depth in their scientific knowledge and professional skills■ 解決研究問題的能力
培養學生具備獨立思考與從事分子醫學相關研究領域的能力 Problem-solving skills
To train students to become independent thinkers  capable of conducting independent and innovative research in molecular medicine 

課程概述 Course Description
       此課程提供博碩士班學生對感染性疾病及癌症研究課題有更深入的瞭解。每一位授課老師將導引學生深入其研究領域、假說及實驗設計，包含對實驗方法學的批判、資料分析及結果解釋。此課程鼓勵學生參與分醫所授課老師的領域以增強跨領域之訓練與學習 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    To inspire and familiarize enrolled IMM students with updated research topics on infectious disease and molecular medicine, which include advanced cancer, viruses, and microbes related researches. IMM students enrolled in this class are encouraged to rotate in different topics for possible interdisciplinary training purpose.
     

